overview: Belly up to the bar, boys! Bartender Paul Chaplin makes good on his promise with the name of his bar - Bar Bangers! Step right up for a second serving of the sexiest bar you will ever visit. Hot sluts like Kyla Croft and Kate Jones server it up on their knees and on the bar. You will be banging your glass for more! The bar is open, gents!
title: Bar Bangers 2
